[SPEAKER_01] kako je on,

530
00:34:36,679 --> 00:34:38,059
[SPEAKER_01] on je bio ono u nesvijesti,

531
00:34:38,059 --> 00:34:41,199
[SPEAKER_01] i on otvori ploću groba,

532
00:34:41,199 --> 00:34:42,360
[SPEAKER_01] izvadi ga vani,

533
00:34:42,360 --> 00:34:43,420
[SPEAKER_01] i ovaj oživi,

534
00:34:43,420 --> 00:34:44,500
[SPEAKER_01] i ovaj lud na njega,

535
00:34:44,500 --> 00:34:46,760
[SPEAKER_01] šta si me mako iz groba?

536
00:34:46,760 --> 00:34:49,079
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, tamo sam trebao umrijeti

537
00:34:49,079 --> 00:34:50,639
[SPEAKER_01] i ti me opet oživiš.

538
00:34:50,639 --> 00:34:52,199
[SPEAKER_01] Vrati me nazad.

539
00:34:52,199 --> 00:34:55,199
[SPEAKER_01] I kaže, ne dirajte ploću dok...

540
00:34:55,199 --> 00:34:57,579
[SPEAKER_01] I on je probeo vrijeme u grobu

541
00:34:57,579 --> 00:34:58,639
[SPEAKER_01] i pobjedio je sve.

542
00:34:58,639 --> 00:35:00,820
[SPEAKER_01] Posljedica toga,

543
00:35:00,820 --> 00:35:02,460
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je u tišini s Bogom

544
00:35:02,460 --> 00:35:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] pobjedio sebe prije svega,

545
00:35:04,000 --> 00:35:06,159
[SPEAKER_01] posljedica toga je da je on

546
00:35:06,159 --> 00:35:08,519
[SPEAKER_01] iz te pustinje vratio se u svijet

547
00:35:08,519 --> 00:35:10,320
[SPEAKER_01] i gdje god je išao,

548
00:35:10,320 --> 00:35:13,239
[SPEAKER_01] događala su se čudesa.

549
00:35:13,239 --> 00:35:16,019
[SPEAKER_01] A da on nije uopće rekao a...

550
00:35:16,019 --> 00:35:19,519
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, njegova pojava je bila toliko sveta

551
00:35:19,519 --> 00:35:23,159
[SPEAKER_01] da je on prolazio kroz narode,

552
00:35:23,159 --> 00:35:24,659
[SPEAKER_01] kroz gradove,

553
00:35:24,659 --> 00:35:26,900
[SPEAKER_01] ljudi su u njegovoj prisutnosti

554
00:35:26,900 --> 00:35:27,739
[SPEAKER_01] ozdravljali.

555
00:35:27,739 --> 00:35:29,400
[SPEAKER_01] On je samo pogledao,

556
00:35:29,400 --> 00:35:30,659
[SPEAKER_01] oslobađali se.

557
00:35:30,659 --> 00:35:31,460
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže,

558
00:35:31,460 --> 00:35:32,860
[SPEAKER_01] najveći čudotvorac,

559
00:35:32,860 --> 00:35:34,039
[SPEAKER_01] ali zašto?

560
00:35:34,039 --> 00:35:36,320
[SPEAKER_01] Zato što je totalno se predao Bogu

561
00:35:36,320 --> 00:35:37,340
[SPEAKER_01] u tišini,

562
00:35:37,340 --> 00:35:38,059
[SPEAKER_01] evo me,

563
00:35:38,059 --> 00:35:38,599
[SPEAKER_01] ja i ti.

564
00:35:39,139 --> 00:35:40,519
[SPEAKER_01] I on se preobrazio

565
00:35:40,519 --> 00:35:41,900
[SPEAKER_01] u drugog Krista.

566
00:35:41,900 --> 00:35:44,260
[SPEAKER_01] On je bio taj Krist

567
00:35:44,260 --> 00:35:45,420
[SPEAKER_01] koji je išao među narode

568
00:35:45,420 --> 00:35:46,780
[SPEAKER_01] i činio čudesa.

569
00:35:46,780 --> 00:35:48,860
[SPEAKER_01] Čovjek koji je živio pustinjom.

570
00:35:48,860 --> 00:35:52,059
[SPEAKER_00] O, Bože moj.

571
00:35:52,059 --> 00:35:56,300
[SPEAKER_01] Ilija.

572
00:35:56,300 --> 00:35:58,340
[SPEAKER_01] Sveti Ilija.

573
00:35:58,340 --> 00:36:00,260
[SPEAKER_01] Zaštitnik Bosne i Hercegovina,

574
00:36:00,260 --> 00:36:01,179
[SPEAKER_01] ako niste znali.

575
00:36:01,179 --> 00:36:04,280
[SPEAKER_01] Znam da na novo rođeni imaju misiju

576
00:36:04,280 --> 00:36:05,780
[SPEAKER_01] za mir u Bosni i Hercegovini.

577
00:36:05,780 --> 00:36:07,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ilija je zaštitnik.

578
00:36:08,460 --> 00:36:10,780
[SPEAKER_01] I on govori o tom Bogu.

579
00:36:10,780 --> 00:36:12,500
[SPEAKER_01] Kako Bog govori?

580
00:36:12,500 --> 00:36:15,619
[SPEAKER_01] I kaže sve to pismo.

581
00:36:15,619 --> 00:36:17,039
[SPEAKER_01] Nije bio u potresu,

582
00:36:17,039 --> 00:36:18,239
[SPEAKER_01] nije bio u oluji,

583
00:36:18,239 --> 00:36:19,539
[SPEAKER_01] nije bio ovdje,

584
00:36:19,539 --> 00:36:20,159
[SPEAKER_01] ali ondje.

585
00:36:20,159 --> 00:36:22,860
[SPEAKER_01] Bio je u šapatu.

586
00:36:22,860 --> 00:36:27,380
[SPEAKER_00] Bio je u šapatu.

587
00:36:27,380 --> 00:36:30,099
[SPEAKER_00] Jer vi mene čujete?

588
00:36:30,099 --> 00:36:32,980
[SPEAKER_00] Neki da, neki ne.

589
00:36:32,980 --> 00:36:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] A zašto mene čujete?

590
00:36:35,000 --> 00:36:37,039
[SPEAKER_00] Jer niste pozorni.

591
00:36:37,659 --> 00:36:38,539
[SPEAKER_00] šta ja govorim?

592
00:36:38,539 --> 00:36:41,539
[SPEAKER_01] Šalim se.

593
00:36:41,539 --> 00:36:45,599
[SPEAKER_01] Šapat.

594
00:36:45,599 --> 00:36:47,980
[SPEAKER_01] A da bi ti čuo šapat,

595
00:36:47,980 --> 00:36:50,579
[SPEAKER_01] onda moraš biti fokusiran.

596
00:36:52,699 --> 00:36:54,260
[SPEAKER_01] da nema mikrofona,

597
00:36:54,260 --> 00:36:56,360
[SPEAKER_01] oni koji su vani na kiši,

598
00:36:56,360 --> 00:36:57,659
[SPEAKER_01] ne bi me čuli.

599
00:36:57,659 --> 00:36:59,440
[SPEAKER_01] a i ovako me ne slušaju,

600
00:36:59,440 --> 00:37:00,619
[SPEAKER_01] se bore proti kiša.

601
00:37:00,619 --> 00:37:07,739
[SPEAKER_01] Njegov šapat ili Boži šapat ili Božja tišina

602
00:37:07,739 --> 00:37:12,619
[SPEAKER_01] nadglasava buku svijeta u kojem mi živimo.

603
00:37:13,760 --> 00:37:15,539
[SPEAKER_01] Htio bi ovo još nešto reći,

604
00:37:15,539 --> 00:37:17,440
[SPEAKER_01] koliko imam vremena,

605
00:37:17,440 --> 00:37:17,840
[SPEAKER_01] dobre,

606
00:37:17,840 --> 00:37:20,440
[SPEAKER_01] još sam u gabaritima,

607
00:37:20,440 --> 00:37:22,760
[SPEAKER_01] a tek sam prvu stranicu izgledio,

608
00:37:22,760 --> 00:37:25,699
[SPEAKER_01] šta sam pripremio.

609
00:37:27,699 --> 00:37:28,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je čudo.

610
00:37:28,699 --> 00:37:30,679
[SPEAKER_01] Mobitel, tako,

611
00:37:30,679 --> 00:37:31,619
[SPEAKER_01] svi imamo mobitel,

612
00:37:31,619 --> 00:37:32,179
[SPEAKER_01] više manje,

613
00:37:32,179 --> 00:37:35,820
[SPEAKER_01] ja mislim da nema od malih do velikih mobitela.

614
00:37:39,699 --> 00:37:41,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo može postati idol.

615
00:37:41,500 --> 00:37:44,199
[SPEAKER_01] Idol.

616
00:37:44,199 --> 00:37:46,360
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto?

617
00:37:46,360 --> 00:37:48,500
[SPEAKER_01] Uvijek je uz mene.

618
00:37:48,500 --> 00:37:52,159
[SPEAKER_01] Uvijek moram ne,

619
00:37:52,159 --> 00:37:53,480
[SPEAKER_01] koliko je vrijeme,

620
00:37:53,480 --> 00:37:54,579
[SPEAKER_01] jer kiša pada,

621
00:37:54,579 --> 00:37:54,940
[SPEAKER_01] kažu,

622
00:37:54,940 --> 00:37:56,940
[SPEAKER_01] kiša će prestati za pola sata.

623
00:37:56,940 --> 00:37:58,239
[SPEAKER_01] Više on zna.

624
00:37:58,239 --> 00:37:59,980
[SPEAKER_01] Mamo dalje.

625
00:37:59,980 --> 00:38:02,760
[SPEAKER_01] Čak me i sluša.

626
00:38:02,760 --> 00:38:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Iako ja toga nisam svijest,

627
00:38:05,000 --> 00:38:05,719
[SPEAKER_01] on me sluša.

628
00:38:05,719 --> 00:38:08,099
[SPEAKER_01] Samo sam ja počeo govorit,

629
00:38:08,099 --> 00:38:08,900
[SPEAKER_01] ajde molim te,

630
00:38:08,900 --> 00:38:09,679
[SPEAKER_01] kad već slušaš,

631
00:38:09,679 --> 00:38:11,440
[SPEAKER_01] onda mi daj neke pobožne stvari.

632
00:38:11,440 --> 00:38:12,780
[SPEAKER_01] Nemo mi davati reklame.

633
00:38:12,780 --> 00:38:16,179
[SPEAKER_01] Neki dan smo pričali,

634
00:38:16,179 --> 00:38:18,119
[SPEAKER_01] žena i ja,

635
00:38:18,119 --> 00:38:19,119
[SPEAKER_01] o nekom parfemu.

636
00:38:19,119 --> 00:38:24,619
[SPEAKER_01] Moraš ženi kupiti dar,

637
00:38:24,619 --> 00:38:25,179
[SPEAKER_01] poklon,

638
00:38:25,179 --> 00:38:26,340
[SPEAKER_01] obradovat.

639
00:38:26,340 --> 00:38:29,500
[SPEAKER_01] I pričam o tom parfemu

640
00:38:29,500 --> 00:38:32,599
[SPEAKER_01] i za 20 minuta

641
00:38:32,599 --> 00:38:34,980
[SPEAKER_01] oglasi taj parfem.

642
00:38:37,559 --> 00:38:38,179
[SPEAKER_01] sluša.

643
00:38:38,179 --> 00:38:43,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ja mislim da mi stojimo

644
00:38:43,539 --> 00:38:44,900
[SPEAKER_01] u životu

645
00:38:44,900 --> 00:38:46,179
[SPEAKER_01] između ekrana

646
00:38:46,179 --> 00:38:47,019
[SPEAKER_01] i Boga.

647
00:38:47,019 --> 00:38:49,440
[SPEAKER_01] I da je tu bitka.

648
00:38:49,440 --> 00:38:51,739
[SPEAKER_01] Čak i na klanjanjima je

649
00:38:51,739 --> 00:38:52,199
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj

650
00:38:52,199 --> 00:38:54,360
[SPEAKER_01] aparat s nama

651
00:38:54,360 --> 00:38:56,480
[SPEAKER_01] i više ga koristimo

652
00:38:56,480 --> 00:38:57,679
[SPEAKER_01] nego da gledamo Boga.

653
00:38:57,679 --> 00:39:01,300
[SPEAKER_01] A kad uđeš u molitu,

654
00:39:01,300 --> 00:39:02,559
[SPEAKER_01] baš sam pričao sa Josipom,

655
00:39:02,559 --> 00:39:03,780
[SPEAKER_01] neki dan,

656
00:39:03,780 --> 00:39:04,699
[SPEAKER_01] kad uđeš u molitu,

657
00:39:05,119 --> 00:39:06,539
[SPEAKER_01] zatvori vrata svoje sobe.

658
00:39:06,539 --> 00:39:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo treba

659
00:39:08,000 --> 00:39:09,300
[SPEAKER_01] ostati van

660
00:39:09,300 --> 00:39:10,840
[SPEAKER_01] tvoje sobe

661
00:39:10,840 --> 00:39:12,420
[SPEAKER_01] kad ideš sa Gospodinom.

662
00:39:12,420 --> 00:39:13,219
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto?

663
00:39:13,219 --> 00:39:15,400
[SPEAKER_01] Koliko god ti možda

664
00:39:15,400 --> 00:39:17,099
[SPEAKER_01] koristio i trebati

665
00:39:17,099 --> 00:39:18,860
[SPEAKER_01] i stvarno može biti

666
00:39:18,860 --> 00:39:20,460
[SPEAKER_01] alati, evangelizacije

667
00:39:20,460 --> 00:39:22,440
[SPEAKER_01] i zapisati sve,

668
00:39:22,440 --> 00:39:24,880
[SPEAKER_01] ti kad uđeš u molitu,

669
00:39:24,880 --> 00:39:27,440
[SPEAKER_01] ako ja bar imam

670
00:39:27,440 --> 00:39:28,340
[SPEAKER_01] tako svjedočanstvo,

671
00:39:28,340 --> 00:39:29,519
[SPEAKER_01] danas mi se to dogodilo,

672
00:39:29,519 --> 00:39:31,119
[SPEAKER_01] ja molim za ovaj susret

673
00:39:31,119 --> 00:39:33,019
[SPEAKER_01] i mobitel je ostao u sobi

674
00:39:33,019 --> 00:39:35,480
[SPEAKER_01] i nisam isključio zvuk.

675
00:39:35,480 --> 00:39:37,699
[SPEAKER_01] I sad počinje,

676
00:39:37,699 --> 00:39:38,280
[SPEAKER_01] Bože,

677
00:39:38,280 --> 00:39:40,619
[SPEAKER_01] molim te za ovu zajednicu,

678
00:39:40,619 --> 00:39:41,519
[SPEAKER_01] za ovaj susret,

679
00:39:41,519 --> 00:39:41,840
[SPEAKER_01] za ovaj,

680
00:39:41,840 --> 00:39:44,099
[SPEAKER_01] tan, tan, tan, tan, tan, tan.

681
00:39:44,099 --> 00:39:46,059
[SPEAKER_01] Isključim zvuk,

682
00:39:46,059 --> 00:39:46,420
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

683
00:39:46,420 --> 00:39:47,920
[SPEAKER_01] izgasim poziv

684
00:39:47,920 --> 00:39:48,840
[SPEAKER_01] i opet,

685
00:39:48,840 --> 00:39:49,219
[SPEAKER_01] tan, tan,

686
00:39:49,219 --> 00:39:49,880
[SPEAKER_01] pip,

687
00:39:49,880 --> 00:39:52,340
[SPEAKER_01] ako je poroko poslao sada,

688
00:39:52,340 --> 00:39:53,400
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

689
00:39:53,400 --> 00:39:55,539
[SPEAKER_01] zlo on može koristiti

690
00:39:55,539 --> 00:39:56,039
[SPEAKER_01] mobitel

691
00:39:56,039 --> 00:39:58,139
[SPEAKER_01] da te odvrati

692
00:39:58,139 --> 00:39:59,739
[SPEAKER_01] od onoga što trebaš činiti

693
00:39:59,739 --> 00:40:00,940
[SPEAKER_01] i raditi.

694
00:40:00,940 --> 00:40:02,019
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

695
00:40:02,019 --> 00:40:04,219
[SPEAKER_01] često taj mobitel

696
00:40:04,219 --> 00:40:05,360
[SPEAKER_01] zauzima mjesto

697
00:40:05,360 --> 00:40:06,880
[SPEAKER_01] naše tišine

698
00:40:06,880 --> 00:40:07,519
[SPEAKER_01] pred Bogom.

699
00:40:07,519 --> 00:40:08,079
[SPEAKER_01] Često.

700
00:40:08,079 --> 00:40:10,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ako idem na klanjanje,

701
00:40:10,880 --> 00:40:12,639
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

702
00:40:12,639 --> 00:40:14,679
[SPEAKER_01] sigurno,

703
00:40:14,679 --> 00:40:16,239
[SPEAKER_01] veliki broj vremena

704
00:40:16,239 --> 00:40:17,739
[SPEAKER_01] provodim u tišini.

705
00:40:17,739 --> 00:40:19,300
[SPEAKER_01] A mali broj,

706
00:40:19,300 --> 00:40:20,400
[SPEAKER_01] ako mi šta dođe,

707
00:40:20,400 --> 00:40:21,800
[SPEAKER_01] onda ga uzmeni zapišen.

708
00:40:21,800 --> 00:40:23,440
[SPEAKER_01] I pokušavam ga,

709
00:40:23,440 --> 00:40:24,099
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

710
00:40:24,099 --> 00:40:25,019
[SPEAKER_01] maknuti izbije,

711
00:40:25,280 --> 00:40:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] da ga uopće

712
00:40:26,000 --> 00:40:27,219
[SPEAKER_01] negleda ni nekoristiti.

713
00:40:27,219 --> 00:40:29,159
[SPEAKER_01] Zato što te može

714
00:40:29,159 --> 00:40:30,039
[SPEAKER_01] odvratiti

715
00:40:30,039 --> 00:40:30,599
[SPEAKER_01] od onoga,

716
00:40:30,599 --> 00:40:32,260
[SPEAKER_01] od onoga šta je.

717
00:40:32,260 --> 00:40:37,099
[SPEAKER_01] Ono što je,

718
00:40:37,099 --> 00:40:37,820
[SPEAKER_01] što je,

719
00:40:37,820 --> 00:40:39,679
[SPEAKER_01] nekako meni na srcu

720
00:40:39,679 --> 00:40:41,179
[SPEAKER_01] da i podijelim

721
00:40:41,179 --> 00:40:41,960
[SPEAKER_01] sa vama,

722
00:40:41,960 --> 00:40:43,199
[SPEAKER_01] je

723
00:40:43,199 --> 00:40:45,019
[SPEAKER_01] ta,

724
00:40:45,019 --> 00:40:46,119
[SPEAKER_01] ta

725
00:40:46,119 --> 00:40:47,699
[SPEAKER_01] čežnja

726
00:40:47,699 --> 00:40:48,159
[SPEAKER_01] za,

727
00:40:48,159 --> 00:40:50,280
[SPEAKER_01] za tim Božjim stvarima

728
00:40:50,280 --> 00:40:51,639
[SPEAKER_01] i

729
00:40:51,639 --> 00:40:53,260
[SPEAKER_01] tom tišinom,

730
00:40:53,260 --> 00:40:54,519
[SPEAKER_01] pogotovo u sluškivanju

731
00:40:54,519 --> 00:40:55,460
[SPEAKER_01] Božje,

732
00:40:55,460 --> 00:40:56,619
[SPEAKER_01] Božje riječi.

733
00:40:56,619 --> 00:40:58,400
[SPEAKER_01] Ono što

734
00:40:58,400 --> 00:41:00,079
[SPEAKER_01] bi trebalo,

735
00:41:00,079 --> 00:41:00,920
[SPEAKER_01] vam reći,

736
00:41:00,920 --> 00:41:02,019
[SPEAKER_01] njegovat,

737
00:41:02,019 --> 00:41:04,900
[SPEAKER_01] vidim da molite

738
00:41:04,900 --> 00:41:06,139
[SPEAKER_01] i da imate tu,

739
00:41:06,139 --> 00:41:07,760
[SPEAKER_01] tu karizmu,

740
00:41:07,760 --> 00:41:09,059
[SPEAKER_01] molite u jezicima,

741
00:41:09,059 --> 00:41:10,360
[SPEAKER_01] to je

742
00:41:10,360 --> 00:41:11,519
[SPEAKER_01] jedan način

743
00:41:11,519 --> 00:41:12,239
[SPEAKER_01] da dođete

744
00:41:12,239 --> 00:41:13,840
[SPEAKER_01] što brže

745
00:41:13,840 --> 00:41:14,619
[SPEAKER_01] u Božju

746
00:41:14,619 --> 00:41:15,599
[SPEAKER_01] prisutnost.

747
00:41:16,599 --> 00:41:17,260
[SPEAKER_01] imaš problem

748
00:41:17,260 --> 00:41:18,980
[SPEAKER_01] sa fokusiranjem,

749
00:41:18,980 --> 00:41:20,059
[SPEAKER_01] rastrešenošću,

750
00:41:20,059 --> 00:41:21,139
[SPEAKER_01] ako imaš dar jezika,

